Package ma02_resources.participants

Interface Participant

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Facilitator, Partner, Student
    public interface Participant
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    This interface represents a Participant in the CBL. Attributes: name, email and instituition are mandatory. The rest are optional. If these attributes are not provided, an illegalArgumentException must be thrown at instantiation.
